#. §3: `lemma`
#. §4: `rw [lemma]`
#. §5: `l`
#. §6: `r`
#. §7: `rw [lemma] at h`
#. §8: `l`
#. §9: `h`
#. §10: `r`
#: Game.Metadata
msgid "§0 stands for rewrite. Let §1 and §2 be the left and right hand sides of some §3, then §4 replaces every instance of §5 in the goal with §6. We can also do §7 to replace every instance of §8 in the hypothesis §9 with §10."
msgstr ""

