#: Game
msgid "# Welcome to Abstract Algebra, the Game!\n"
"\n"
"This course is a basic introduction of undergraduate-level Abstract Algebra in Lean. We will cover structures such as groups, rings, integral domains, and fields, as well as relations between them like homomorphisms and isomorphisms.\n"
"\n"
"**Important**: Please note that this course is unfinished and made by [an undergraduate](https://www.linkedin.com/in/advayth-pashupati/), and should be taken with a grain of salt."
msgstr ""

